1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4
{ For explanations, check the informationalIntroduction to chapter } 2... g6
{ The is the most common move, played around 35% of the time. Now we're in territory that could also arise from 1... g6.  After moves like 2... e6 and 2... c6, we play 3. e3 and Black has nothing better than transpose to our second chapter - The Retí Gambit: Declined - with the move d5.  Other lesser - and weaker - tries are only mentioned in the tactics chapter, so make sure to check it out! }
3. d4
