{ For explanations, check the informational variation below.  Introduction to chapter }
2... Nc6
{ This is the most played move by Black, but most other moves can also transpose. }
3. d4
{ Following through with our plan, grabbing space in the center and preparing to recapture our d-pawn with our c-pawn. White already scores 56% from this point! }
