{ Very nice start! Getting tempo on the queen and getting the pawn one step further in the center. }
8... Qd6 { Other options don't change the result much. } 9. d4
{ A great finish!  White has a picture-perfect center, the only issue is c5 breaking it down and making it more vulnerable.  This is, however, still a good position for White - especially with the awkward Black pieces. }
