1. Nf3 f5 2. e4 fxe4 3. Ng5 Nf6 4. d3 exd3 5. Bxd3 g6 6. h4 d5 7. h5 Nxh5
{ This is a game losing blunder by Black, also mentioned in the variationThe Dutch 1... f5
  Can you remember how to punish it? }
8. Rxh5
{ Very well done! This brilliant move opens up the light squares too much around the Black king for them to survive. }
8... gxh5 9. Qxh5+ Kd7 10. Nf7
{ Now Black has to give up their queen to not allow the text move. } 10... Qe8
11. Qxd5#
{ Very well done! I hope you didn't fall for   11.Nxh8??  Qxh5  As that would go from mate in 1 to losing your queen! }
