[Result "*"]

1. --
{ This chapter is a result of a contest which I dubbed 'March Model Game Challenge' held in March, 2022.   The contest was a celebration of the launch of my first ever Chessable course  (this one!)  and gave students of the course the opportunity to send in their best games of the month for a chance for them to be featured in this very chapter.  As of such, all the model games that you'll see in this chapter have been played in a single month by students of this course and should therefore show you what to expect in your games!  I hope this will not only aid in your understanding of how you can play the opening, but also inspire you to get your own great wins, like the ones of these students in this chapter! }
